'''Clondex''' was a medicine instrumental in keeping the sufferers of [[Zithrom's syndrome|Zithrom's Disease]] alive. The drug, however, was not a complete cure.<ref name="Do No Harm">{{JournalCite|10|Do No Harm}}</ref> Clondex, combined with [[Iotramine]], was able to regulate an enzyme eruption in the third [[Heart/Legends|heart]] of a [[Pui-ui]].<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

